    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We decided early on that topics do not belong in ENRs. In the discv5 data model, ENRs are stored in the topic table. If we want to support some kind of *pre-registration* for topics without an explicit `REGTOPIC`, the topics would need to be sent alongside the ENR, or in `PING`.",
